description:
Re-added the drums in, made small changes so it would fit (including painstakingly redoing the track without repeats to match the newer revision) but I mostly just copied it from the first revision, so the notation is wrong in a lot of places

Also added a distortion guitar track for the middle instead of overdrive because it's supposed to be full volume
title: 10000 Days Wings Part 2

description:
Pretty much redone everything. (except the drums)
I had to start from the ground up because I had to sync the tab up to the song which required a lot of tempo fiddling.
Cleaned up the bass section quite a lot, some notes were wrong or missing, I've got it pretty much perfect I think.

Also redone the guitar from the ground up, I spent a while noodling around to find the best place on the fretboard to play the different parts and getting as many of the intricacies right too.

If anybody knows how to tab out drums, please feel free to edit my file and add them on.
Hope everybody enjoys!
title: 10000 Days Wings Part 2
